  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n\r\n## Problem \r\nThe wallet user avatar has, at least, the following problems:\r\n\r\n- Its circle is always in a 50 custom color variant regardless of the theme selected.\r\n- It's not using the `with-theme` fn.\r\n- The sizes received by its API are not following our current standard (a `:size-NN` keyword).\r\n\r\nThis issue consists of improving the implementation and spot and fix any other possible problem.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nWe want that the component is looking as designs:\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/WQZcp6S0EnzxdTL4taoKDv/Design-System-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=114-7648&mode=dev\r\nand match our guidelines and standards for components\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
